What is Raven BuJo?

Glad you asked! Raven BuJo to-do app based on the bullet journal method.
Okay... but what is the bullet journal method?
The bullet journal method is... Created by...
What makes this app different from any other to-do or project mangement apps?
To be honest, in it's current state, not much if anything. I had planned to do more, but was unable to get to it in time.
Okay... so what features do you have to offer?
Raven BuJo offers three coloumn list view. Simple to add, edit, and delete tasks. Task priorities are easily seen so you know what to focus on. Your deadlines printed on the task card so you don't have to search around when you have something due to be completed soon.
